{"tid":1788991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"这支球队的人，有黑黄白皮肤，这么有层次！","createTime":"2019-12-19T06:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T08:29:59.000Z","uid":165817,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04fc9623e4b0d05672ff24e113173e63b9fffb58","tid":1788991,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"記唔記得早幾年我地俾大陸串<br />\n話港隊有法圖斯 黃洋 施利呢啲歸化兵<br />\n「這支球隊的人，有黑皮膚，有黃皮膚，有白皮膚，這麼有層次，得防著點！」<br />\n<br />\n點知幾年之後<br />\n大陸啲歸化兵一個一個咁加落去<br />\n年頭有個大陸都未去過 中文都唔識隻嘅英格蘭恩拿利斯<br />\n幾個月前到巴西嘅艾傑臣<br />\n今日新鮮出爐有高拿特<br />\n跟住仲話想招埋干卡個仔<br />\n<br />\n以前就串港隊招啲非華裔<br />\n而家就懶係溫情咁話大家都係一家人 一齊幫中國努力入世界盃<br />\n施利五歲就嚟咗香港 麥基十歲<br />\n恩拿利斯成世仔都喺英國就叫埋人做李可<br />\n你話笑死唔笑死"},{"pid":"0aa2a0bccfabfd2bfe63df5894e479672cb7e015","tid":1788991,"uid":12006,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"大陸狗係咁on9架啦"},{"pid":"2b15a5ae34ef0f97b6f9f8e3d57942ee49b6f6e9","tid":1788991,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0aa2a0bccfabfd2bfe63df5894e479672cb7e015","tid":1788991,"uid":12006,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"大陸狗係咁on9架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"咁想招啲英國佬巴西佬 幾年前就唔好撩人啦"},{"pid":"c77031c0cdc9f8529ac8550104e4ecfdc6394dce","tid":1788991,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:40:18.000Z","msg":"鄧主席：不管白貓還是黑貓，捉到老鼠就是好貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3ed64a9159a3f8156aa6df86abe97e1f8e8ed8","tid":1788991,"uid":33730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:42:00.000Z","msg":"中國國家隊的人，有巴西人，有英國人，這麼有層次，得防著點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fdab84b001dcae92f15488719a70aadd74acb0","tid":1788991,"uid":139573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"巴西自亙古以來就係我大中華嘅領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9c6f214a0ac81d8e76fb24038b2edbb585a6ab","tid":1788991,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13fdab84b001dcae92f15488719a70aadd74acb0","tid":1788991,"uid":139573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"巴西自亙古以來就係我大中華嘅領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:29:59.000Z","msg":"Sorly我國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來只係攞返屬於自己嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}